              <li>Full room hire from Ksh 5,000</li>
              <li>Custom menu available</li>
              <li>Projector and screen included</li>
              <li>Dedicated waitstaff</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-warning mt-2">Book a Room</a>
          </div>
        </div>

