            <p>Get freshly roasted Kenyan coffee beans delivered to your door every week or month. Choose your roast level and grind size.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>250g bag from Ksh 800/month</li>
              <li>Nyeri, Kirinyaga, or Murang'a origin</li>
              <li>Free delivery within Nairobi</li>
              <li>Cancel anytime</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-warning mt-2">Subscribe Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>

