            <p>Learn to brew great coffee from our professional baristas. We offer beginner and advanced classes every Saturday morning.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>2-hour beginner class — Ksh 1,500</li>
              <li>Full day advanced course — Ksh 4,000</li>
              <li>Certificate provided</li>
              <li>Maximum 8 students per class</li>
            </ul>
